name: Survival 3d Craft Labyrinth
description:
Enter the labyrinth and try to survive!

Survival 3d Craft Labyrinth is one of the most addictive maze games in the world!
Your main goal in this game is to try to survive in this labyrinth!
Go and start your wonderful adventure in this cube world!
Look behind every corner and find a key and then run away as fast as you can!

Survival 3d Craft Labyrinth game features:
+ Addictive maze run gameplay
+ Beautiful cube world
+ Logic puzzle and action game

Enter the labyrinth and find an exit! Good luck!
